description: This continuation of Mathematics 122 covers the material in Mathematics 126 in greater depth and includes supplementary material. Prerequisite: Mathematics 122, or Mathematics 119 or 120 and permission of the instructor, or Mathematics Placement Recommendation. Credit may be earned for either Mathematics 126 or 128, but not both.
